The files in this folder:

1. weather.html - Is a template which outputs the weather conditions to the client
2. getWeather.sh - This script downloads the HTML page containing the weather conditions from the BOM. This can be swapped for a C program or a PHP script. It redownloads the web page every hour
3. w.d - This is the HTML page that the above script downloads
4. Weather.js - This script parses the downloaded file and extracts the variables we want

How to use:

Start getWeather.sh on the command line

Use JQUERY to put the variables below into nice places on the web page

todayTemp
todayCondition
todayRainChance
tomorrowMinTemp
tomorrowMaxTemp
tomorrowRainChance
tomorrowPrecip
tomorrowCondition
